data.description: Call today to see this 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch home in Country Aire Estates. Open concept with cathedral ceiling in the living room. Main bedroom ensuite with dual sinks and walk-in closet. Updated kitchen appliances, newer gas water heater and a finished basement with a wet bar for entertaining. Main level laundry hookup. The fenced in backyard offers a pergola and above ground pool for those family memories. Sellers offering AHS Essential Warranty.
